<div class="white_box_shadow">
<p class="geolocation-title" align="center">*Terms and Conditions</p>
<p>Valid on NEW BOOKINGS made between 25th September and 31st December 2017 ONLY.</p>
<p>FREE 1st class return rail upgrade from a 2nd class return transfer ticket.</p>
<p>Offer applies to all Zurich airport flights arriving any day of the week and some Geneva airport flights (arriving all day Sunday-Friday and between 12:00-16:00 on Saturdays).</p>
<p>Offer applies to all holiday durations in Switzerland including short break holidays.</p>
<p>Offer excludes holidays to Verbier.</p>
<p>Rail tickets are non-refundable.</p>
<p>Guests flying into Geneva airport on Saturdays will have an option to travel by coach transfer although there may be a long wait and unused rail tickets will not be reimbursed.</p>
